{"tid":2391490,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(推到完場 4)SpaceX Starship SN9 Test Flight — FAA我屌你老母","createTime":"2021-02-02T09:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T09:08:59.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d3be1887e3c97ffadaabe5e7de022bd033c9ca74","tid":2391490,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"兩星期內第四次嘗試高空測試，希望真係飛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wfHqbahPKpY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwfHqbahPKpY&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=e80f3e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wfHqbahPKpY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ky5l9ZxsG9M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKy5l9ZxsG9M&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=0e196d6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ky5l9ZxsG9M</a><br />\n<br />\nSN8 Recap<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_qwLHlVjRyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_qwLHlVjRyw&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=e025243f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_qwLHlVjRyw</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>常見問題︰</strong><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 星艦係由兩個部份組成，上層的starship同下層的助推器superheavy。當整支星艦去到軌道後助推器superheavy便會分離返回地球，starship則視任務而定會否在軌道接受多次加油，還是直接飛住目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8JyvzU0CXU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC8JyvzU0CXU&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=dad4f886\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8JyvzU0CXU</a><br />\n<br />\n &mdash; 星艦系統將會係人類歷史上除土星5號外最大型的火箭，同時都係第一支完成可重用的火箭，現時的獵鷹9號及重型獵鷹只是一級推重器及有整流罩可重用，若星艦成功，其探索成本將有望進一步降低，運載成本也將比獵鷹9號更低<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKnEyHr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKnEyHr.png&h=2c03bd92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 上層的starship既測試原型機SN系列預計會去到SN20，但因為進度比預計快消息指SN12-SN14已被取消，重心放在SN15-SN20，將會有重大更新及更高的高空飛行測試。下部份的BN系列也預計將在年中開始測試，BN1原型機已完工。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OfDgAVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfDgAVR.jpg&h=c13c5db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 星艦不同其他火箭，是由不鏽鋼組成，其強度比碳複合材料高。但其實不鏽鋼正常唔會用係火箭到，因為過重，但elon認為不鏽鋼係低溫同高溫下表現更出色，減去因此少用左既絕緣陶瓦反而成支既重量會更低，而且不鏽鋼的平價同易造令快速生產成為可能。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 藍色起源的所謂可重用火箭不論體積及飛行高度都遠不及獵鷹9號，也無法進入地球軌道，因此獵鷹9號到現時還是世界上唯二的可重用的重型運載火箭。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RQe_I0Zmzuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRQe_I0Zmzuk&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=7f426457\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RQe_I0Zmzuk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZjSTKX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZjSTKX.png&h=c43a17d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73fZyKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73fZyKW.jpg&h=75105e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8GU64W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8GU64W.jpg&h=99743ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vdQR9ig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvdQR9ig.jpg&h=b05db9ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyH9bwB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyH9bwB.jpg&h=7feab108&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"495e8e28131627b6f84ca040eeb256076084ea38","tid":2391490,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"錯台sor"},{"pid":"c6b4d8733b82814a42cb7677866896b50e0441e8","tid":2391490,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ce7932d4501fe67fdb95163804544835a180c8","tid":2391490,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"錯台sor<br />\n(推到完場 4)SpaceX Starship SN9 Test Flight &mdash; FAA我屌你老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2391491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2391491</a>"},{"pid":"88b3afdc893a62fd76d34ca1cd6810a6ff8657b4","tid":2391490,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6b4d8733b82814a42cb7677866896b50e0441e8","tid":2391490,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(推到完場 4)SpaceX Starship SN9 Test Flight &mdash; FAA我屌你老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2391491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2391491</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"71ce7932d4501fe67fdb95163804544835a180c8","tid":2391490,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:08:46.000